overview:
We are your one-stop source for brand name sneakers. DrovedUp.com is a Miami based company that serves domestic and select international destinations with a collection of the most popular nike shoes at low prices. We work closely with manufacturing companies that are contracted withNike, Addidas, Reebok, Timberland and many more. Our inventoryof high quality authentic shoes includes , Nike Air Jordan 3, Nike Air Yeezy, Nike Dunks, Nike SB Dunk, Nike Air 180, Nike Air Max LTD, Nike Basketball Sneakers, Nike Air Max 360 and Nike rare, limited Editions. We also carry Adidas, including Adicolor II, Adidas Country Style, Adidas NBA Superstar and Adidas Adicolor Series, Puma, Reebok, K-Swiss and other popular brands. All shipping costs are included in the price.

We are located in beautiful Miami Gardens, Florida. As stated before we work manufacturing companies that are contracted by Nike, Reebok, Addidas, Timberland, and much more to bring you quality authentic shoes. We are currently only an online store with offices in Miami Gardens, Florida.
